  "instructions": [
    "In a medium saucepan, combine Pasta with water and salt to taste. Bring to a boil.",
    "Cook pasta until al dente; drain and set aside.",
    "Heat Olive Oil in a pan over medium heat. Add Garlic Powder, Red Pepper Flakes, and Aekjeot. Cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add Fish Sauce to the pan with spices. Simmer for another minute.",
    "Fold in drained pasta and Basil. Toss well until evenly coated with sauce.",
    "Serve hot as a main course."
